===Etymology 1===
[[Image:Drinking Bee.jpg|thumb|A bee]]
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|beo|bēo|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|bēō|lang=en}}, from {{proto|Germanic|bhī-|lang=en}}. Cognate with Dutch {{term|bij|lang=nl}}, [[w:Upper German|Upper German]] {{term|Beie|lang=de}}, Swedish {{term|bi|lang=sv}}; and (''from Indo-European'') with Latvian {{term|bite|lang=lv}}, Russian {{term|пчела|tr=pčelá|lang=ru|sc=Cyrl}}, Old Irish {{term|bech|lang=sga}}.

